56:32.188 --> 56:34.157
What're you talking about?

56:34.190 --> 56:34.991
- Did you fucking killer?

56:35.024 --> 56:36.126
I have no idea.

56:36.159 --> 56:37.560
- Who fucking killed her?!

56:37.594 --> 56:39.062
- Who?

56:39.095 --> 56:40.096
- Christine!

56:41.264 --> 56:43.900
